The election has been over for a year and all I keep hearing is the president is insane , must be impeached , has conspired with Russians , is only for the rich , has no compassion , and on and on . Endless utter nonsense ! The voters like what Trump campaigned on and duly elected him . Everything he promised he is trying to deliver . What is so bad about doing what is in America 's interest ? When has any political figure kept his promises ? Never ! The Democrats want America to change . They 're weakening and undermining all our American traditions -- in our schools , churches , police , families , the national anthem , our flag . They want open borders , sanctuary cities and states , demanding constitutional rights for non - citizens . People are destroying monuments and statues , burning , looting , rioting . Has our country gone insane ? The America I knew all my life is quickly fading into something I no longer recognize and is becoming alien to me . I was a lifetime registered Democrat for 65 years and seldom missed voting in elections . The behavior of the Democrats forced me to change my ...
